ivardefs.name: codeFilter_
ivardefs.desc: Code filters specify additional constraints on the data, specifying the value set of interest for a particular element of the data.

ivardefs.name: profile_
ivardefs.desc: The profile of the required data, specified as the uri of the profile definition.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The type of the required data, specified as the type name of a resource. For profiles, this value is set to the type of the base resource of the profile.
